      "text": [
        "هِ عَزَّ وَ جَلَّ «ثُمَّ لْيَقْضُوا تَفَثَهُمْ» قَالَ «قَصُّ اَلشَّارِبِ وَ اَلْأَظْفَارِ »."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3032 - Rabi‘ narrated from Muhammad ibn Muslim, from Abu Ja‘far (as), regarding the saying of Allah (swt), the Almighty: \"Then let them complete their prescribed duties\" (Surah Al-Hajj 22:29).\nImam (as) said: \"It refers to trimming the mustache and cutting the nails.\""
        ]
      }
